>>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. MAIN.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 INPUT-LINE        PIC X(100).
01 A-TEXT            PIC X(20).
01 B-TEXT            PIC X(20).
01 A                 PIC S9(11) COMP-5.
01 B                 PIC S9(11) COMP-5.
01 RESULT            PIC S9(11) COMP-5.
01 RESULT-OUT        PIC -Z(10)9.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    ACCEPT INPUT-LINE
    UNSTRING INPUT-LINE DELIMITED BY ALL SPACES
        INTO A-TEXT B-TEXT
    END-UNSTRING
    MOVE FUNCTION NUMVAL(A-TEXT) TO A
    MOVE FUNCTION NUMVAL(B-TEXT) TO B
    COMPUTE RESULT = A + B
    MOVE RESULT TO RESULT-OUT
    DISPLAY FUNCTION TRIM(RESULT-OUT)
    STOP RUN.